  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个客户端和服务端的连接流程图，核心是登录和保活机制。客户端从Start开始，然后发送REQ_LOGIN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "Client",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "REQ_LOGIN之后是直接走TCP还是UDP？我看到后面有个Send_UDP节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C2",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，C3就是Send_UDP，所有数据包都走UDP。REQ_LOGIN之后进入Send_UDP，然后发到服务端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "S1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Client子图建好了，包含Start、REQ_LOGIN、Send_UDP，还有后面需要的Keepalive和Outgoing_Packets。Server这边先放Recv_Validate_Magic作为入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "C4",
        "C5",
        "S1",
        "Client",
        "Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务端收到后要先验证magic number，无效的包直接丢弃。有效的包再判断是不是登录请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "Drop",
        "S2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Drop节点放在Server子图外面还是里面？另外S2用菱形表示判断可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drop",
        "S2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Drop放在外面吧，表示处理结果。S2用菱形，判断Is REQ_LOGIN?，yes走登录流程，no走RateLimits。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Drop",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Drop节点和判断菱形S2，连接S1到S2。登录流程那边我加上ProcessLogin和RES_LOGIN。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "Drop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "RES_LOGIN之后要回到客户端的Outgoing_Packets，这是关键，表示登录成功后客户端可以正常发包了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S4",
        "C5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
