      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Keepalive定期触发，回到Send_UDP发心跳包。另外C5有两个分支：有数据包时piggyback回S1，没数据时要发Explicit_ACK。",
      "elements_involved": [
